# --- Core Monorepo Rule Extensions ---
**/node_modules/
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/.angular/
**/.vscode/
**/dist/
**/tmp/
**/out-tsc/

# --- .NET Specific Artifacts ---
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.suo
*.userprefs
